Apps att enablea:
blog


Settings:

I config.php, lägg till

$Configuration['Garden']['InputFormatter'] = 'BBcode';
$Configuration['Garden']['Profile']['ShowAbout'] = FALSE;
$Configuration['Garden']['Thumbnail']['Size'] = 100;
$Configuration['Garden']['Locale'] = 'sv-SE';

på rad 39.
